Description:
1. Core Module:
Web Server : main class , accept client requests and distribution
ServerContext : Save URL and name of Servlet class into Map , and use Reflect Theroy instantiate corresponding servlet
ClientHandler: By using Server context , use reflect theroy, execute servlet;
2.Http Module
HttpContext: use dom4j parse XML document which have resource postfix and ContextType.
HttpRequest: include request-line, header, context, and parse them
HttpResponse: include status-line,response header, response context
3 .Servlet Module
HttpServlet : super class which have general characters
RegServlet : processing register service, and save User INFO into data persistence layer
LoginServlet, ChangeServlet
